column2: Starring Woody Harrelson and Wesley Snipes 'White Men Can not Jump' revolves around Billy and Sydney think they're the best basketball players in the city, so when you start playing, nothing can stop them, except each other. To add more problems, Billy owes money and is being chased by a gangster far. The film is directed and written by Ron Shelton and Rosie Perez, Kadeem Hardison, Ernest Harden Jr. John Marshall Jones and Marques Johnson round out the main cast of this comedy.
